room_title: Escape room "Lost Teddy" by Make a Break Escape in Tampa
room_description: Your parents have gone out for supper, and your babysitter has let you stay up past your bedtime. With your parents only 30 minutes away from home, your babysitter has put you to bed, however you know you can’t sleep without your teddy bear, but you can’t remember where in your mess of a room you left it. Can you retrace your steps from the evening of play to find your teddy in time?
